snippet.title: Mortal Kombat 1 - Official Omni-Man Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Allowing a Viltrumite into the Realms? Think, Liu Kang! Think! Omni-Man joins #MK1 starting November 9.

Get the Premium Edition or add the Kombat Pack to your Standard Edition to play as Omni-Man: https://www.mortalkombat.com/purchase

It's In Our Blood. Discover a reborn Mortal Kombat Universe created by Fire God Liu Kang. Mortal Kombat 1 ushers in a new era of the iconic franchise with a new fighting system, game modes, and Fatalities!
